_:Nf5d7090f477f4274a35e30942292f201 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Rebecca has been the Director of the UK Space Agency since April 2026.</p>\n\n<p>Rebecca was previously the Director for Space in DSIT.</p>\n\n<p>Rebecca’s previous roles include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Co-Director for Citizens and Networks, Department for Exiting the European Union</li>\n  <li>Director, International (jobshare), UK Space Agency</li>\n  <li>Deputy Director for Rail Strategy at the Department for Transport</li>\n  <li>Head of the EU Balance of Competences Review, Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs</li>\n  <li>Head of National Adaptation Programme, Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs</li>\n  <li>Head of European Environment Team, Cabinet Office</li>\n  <li>Senior Private Secretary to the Secretary of State for Environment</li>\n  <li>Seconded National Expert, DG Environment</li>\n</ul>\n" .
